@startuml Online OAuth Flow

actor User
participant "Mobile App" as MobileApp
participant "GET /api/auth/shopify" as AuthRoute
participant "Shopify OAuth Endpoint" as ShopifyOAuth
participant "GET /api/auth/shopify/callback" as CallbackRoute

User -> MobileApp: Navigate to /m/login
MobileApp -> AuthRoute: GET /api/auth/shopify
AuthRoute -> AuthRoute: Set shopify_auth_state cookie\nSet shopify_auth_type cookie
AuthRoute -> ShopifyOAuth: Redirect to https://{shop}/admin/oauth/authorize?grant
ShopifyOAuth --> AuthRoute: Redirect back to GET /api/auth/shopify/callback
AuthRoute -> CallbackRoute: Handle callback, verify state, exchange code for token
CallbackRoute --> MobileApp: Authentication successful, set session cookie
User --> MobileApp: Redirected to mobile app with authenticated session
@enduml